simulator lang=spectre
global 0

ahdl_include "logic_vector_assign_slice.vams"

Vcode0 (code0 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 1.0 199n 1.0 200n 0.0 500n 0.0]
Vcode1 (code1 0) vsource dc=0.0
Vcode2 (code2 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0.0 99n 0.0 100n 1.0 299n 1.0 300n 0.0 500n 0.0]
Vcode3 (code3 0) vsource dc=1.0
Vsel (sel 0) vsource type=pwl wave=[0 0.0 99n 0.0 100n 1.0 199n 1.0 200n 0.0 299n 0.0 300n 1.0 500n 1.0]

XDUT (code3 code2 code1 code0 sel y) logic_vector_assign_slice

tran tran stop=500n
save code0 code1 code2 code3 sel y
